'''Owerri''' bụ ịsị óche [[Imo State]]. Dika ịsị óche ndi ewere na obodo [[Naigeria]], '''Owerri''' nwere ọtụtụ madu bi n'ime ya.
Owerri ugbua nwere ụlọ akwukwo di elu nke mere ya obodo akwukwo, ụlọ akwukwo ndịa bụ Federal university nke nka na ụzụ owerri, Federal polytechnic nke Nekede, Imo state university ya na Alvan Ikoku college. Ule agumakwụkwọ di kwa na owerri. Ụlọ akwụkwọ ndịa emela Owerri abụrụ ebe agụma akwụkwọ bụ suru gede.

